commit.message: Added comments and output for better user understanding
Moved java files to correct package (directories)

Implemented Win/Lose conditions, Prevented movement to certain spaces

+ Win at target value
+ Lose if score < 0 or >255
+ Cannot return to previous tile
+ Can only divide perfectly
Added the about menu complete functionailty
Added constraints to begin the grid for the game.

First Draft of Java Files

Most of functionality in Token and Gameboard classes.
Added activities for Stats and About
Added first start to main menu
